## Jack's Photo Caption Contest
Register or login to use application, post, delete, or update captions under the funny photos.

## Getting Started - Local Set Up
First, clone the repository at www.github.com/JackPetersenCode/photocaption. Navigate into the directory and install all necessary dependencies with 'npm install' on your local machine.

Next, create the local database with 'sequelize db:create', this will create a local database named 'photocaptions' on your local machine.

'sequelize db:seed:all' - This will seed your newly created local database with the seeder data in the repository's 'seeder' folder.

'sequelize db:migrate' - This will update the schema in the database and migrate any changes made.

## Getting Started - Use app on Heroku.com
https://jacks-caption-contest.herokuapp.com/

